"You alright wing?" Lunarpine asked, he saw her take the blast, not 
more than a minute after he called her down. (Logo's post came 
through as I was writing mine." In a way he'd never admit to anyone 
he hoped she'd been hurt, It would give him an excuse to rip every 
circuit from the attackers bodies.
